    <p>• Grade 1 Lig­a­ment is stretched, with no torn fi­bres.</p>
    <p>Re­cov­ery is usu­ally four weeks.</p>
    <p>• Grade 2 Par­tial tear of the lig­a­ment. Re­cov­ery can</p>
    <p>take 12 to 16 weeks.</p>
    <p>• Grade 3 Com­plete tear, which re­quires sur­gi­cal in­ter­ven­tion. Re­cover takes at least six months. It de­pends on how well one re­sponds to re­ha­bil­i­ta­tion, as well as if other struc­tures such as bone, car­ti­lage and menis­cus are also dam­aged dur­ing the in­jury.</p>


